                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-indigo-700">
                    1. üìä Netflix Data: Cleaning, Analysis, and Visualization
                </h3>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-700">Difficulty Level:</strong> <span class="text-green-600 font-medium">Intermediate</span></p>
                <p class="mb-3 leading-relaxed">
                    This project delves into a comprehensive Netflix content dataset, employing robust data cleaning techniques to ensure data quality. It then proceeds with an in-depth Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) to uncover fascinating trends in content distribution, popular genres, and the evolution of content additions over time. The project culminates in insightful visualizations that provide a clear narrative of Netflix's content landscape and identifies top contributing directors and countries.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-700">Tools Used:</strong> Python, ML, SQL, Excel</p>
                <p><strong class="text-gray-700">Skills Demonstrated:</strong> Data Cleaning, Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA), Data Visualization, Machine Learning (Conceptual), Python, SQL, Excel.</p>
