                    2. üìà Customer Satisfaction Prediction
                </h3>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-700">Difficulty Level:</strong> <span class="text-green-600 font-medium">Advanced</span></p>
                <p class="mb-3 leading-relaxed">
                    This project focuses on the development of a sophisticated machine learning model designed to predict customer satisfaction. It will involve tackling real-world challenges such as advanced data preprocessing, meticulous feature engineering to extract meaningful signals from raw data, and a systematic approach to model selection, training, and rigorous evaluation. The ultimate goal is to build a highly accurate predictive tool that can potentially inform business strategies for enhanced customer experience and retention.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-700">Tools Used:</strong> VS Code, Jupyter Notebook</p>
                <p><strong class="text-gray-700">Skills Demonstrated:</b> Machine Learning, Python, SQL, Excel, Model Training & Evaluation (e.g., Cross-validation, Hyperparameter Tuning), Feature Engineering, Advanced Data Preprocessing, Predictive Modeling, Performance Metrics Analysis.</p>
